1. Write one of 'receive0' or 'receive1' to the on-board Flash ROM.
2. Load ECO32 into the FPGA.
3. Press and release the ECO32 reset button.
4. Start 'send' on the PC. Choose the serial port according to the serial
   line the board is listening on. After a while 'send' shows either a
   dot ('.') indicating success, or a question mark ('?') for failure.
